'''丽贝卡·史密斯'''（{{lang-en|Rebecca Smith}}，{{bd|2000年|3月14日||}}）生于艾伯塔省红鹿市，是一名加拿大女子游泳运动员，主攻自由泳<ref name="gc2018">{{cite web|title=Rebecca Smith|url=https://results.gc2018.com/en/swimming/athlete-profile-n6022734-rebecca-smith.htm|work=Gold Coast 2018|accessdate=2018-04-08|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191006202925/https://results.gc2018.com/en/swimming/athlete-profile-n6022734-rebecca-smith.htm|archivedate=2019-10-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>。她的姐姐Madalyn同样是一名游泳选手<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.swimming.ca/en/swimmer/rebecca-smith/|title=Rebecca Smith|work=Swimming Canada|accessdate=2020-08-23|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170906114623/https://www.swimming.ca/en/swimmer/rebecca-smith/|archivedate=2017-09-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>。丽贝卡于2018年进入[[多伦多大学|多伦多大学]]修读生命科学专业，同时加入该校的游泳队<ref>{{cite web|url=https://varsityblues.ca/news/2019/7/25/swimming-smith-earns-second-bronze-medal-at-world-championships.aspx|title=SMITH EARNS SECOND BRONZE MEDAL AT WORLD CHAMPIONSHIPS|work=Toronto Varsity Blues|date=2019-07-25|accessdate=2020-08-23|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20200823025452/https://varsityblues.ca/news/2019/7/25/swimming-smith-earns-second-bronze-medal-at-world-championships.aspx|archivedate=2020-08-23}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://oua.ca/aotw/female_aotw_november_19|title=Rebecca Smith, Swimming, Toronto|work=Ontario University Athletics|date=2018-11-19|accessdate=2020-08-23|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20200823025736/https://oua.ca/aotw/female_aotw_november_19|archivedate=2020-08-23}}</ref>。

